  </video>
  <steps>
    <step num="0">Cut mangoes into ½-inch (1.3 cm) cubes and put on baking sheet. Cover and freeze for a minimum of 4 hours. </step>
    <step num="1">In a food processor, add the frozen mango, water, and honey. Mix until the mixture is smooth. </step>
    <step num="2">Remove from food processor and scoop into tray. </step>
    <step num="3">Freeze for one additional hour. </step>
    <step num="4">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
